19static inline isc_result_t
20fromtext_talink(ARGS_FROMTEXT) {
21 isc_token_t token;
22 dns_name_t name;
23 isc_buffer_t buffer;
24 int i;
25
26 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_talink);
27
28 UNUSED(type);
29 UNUSED(rdclass);
30 UNUSED(callbacks);
31
32 if (origin == NULL)
33 origin = dns_rootname;
34
35 for (i = 0; i < 2; i++) {
36 RETERR(isc_lex_getmastertoken(lexer, &token,
37 isc_tokentype_string,
38 false));
39
40 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
41 buffer_fromregion(&buffer, &token.value.as_region);
42 RETTOK(dns_name_fromtext(&name, &buffer, origin,
43 options, target));
44 }
45
46 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
47}
48
49static inline isc_result_t
50totext_talink(ARGS_TOTEXT) {
51 isc_region_t dregion;
52 dns_name_t prev;
53 dns_name_t next;
54 dns_name_t prefix;
55 bool sub;
56
57 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_talink);
58 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
59
60 dns_name_init(&prev, NULL);
61 dns_name_init(&next, NULL);
62 dns_name_init(&prefix, NULL);
63
64 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &dregion);
65
66 dns_name_fromregion(&prev, &dregion);
67 isc_region_consume(&dregion, name_length(&prev));
68
69 dns_name_fromregion(&next, &dregion);
70 isc_region_consume(&dregion, name_length(&next));
71
72 sub = name_prefix(&prev, tctx->origin, &prefix);
73 RETERR(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
74
75 RETERR(str_totext(" ", target));
76
77 sub = name_prefix(&next, tctx->origin, &prefix);
78 return(dns_name_totext(&prefix, sub, target));
79}
80
81static inline isc_result_t
82fromwire_talink(ARGS_FROMWIRE) {
83 dns_name_t prev;
84 dns_name_t next;
85
86 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_talink);
87
88 UNUSED(type);
89 UNUSED(rdclass);
90
91 dns_decompress_setmethods(dctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
92
93 dns_name_init(&prev, NULL);
94 dns_name_init(&next, NULL);
95
96 RETERR(dns_name_fromwire(&prev, source, dctx, options, target));
97 return(dns_name_fromwire(&next, source, dctx, options, target));
98}
99
100static inline isc_result_t
101towire_talink(ARGS_TOWIRE) {
102 isc_region_t sregion;
103 dns_name_t prev;
104 dns_name_t next;
105 dns_offsets_t moffsets;
106 dns_offsets_t roffsets;
107
108 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_talink);
109 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
110
111 dns_compress_setmethods(cctx, DNS_COMPRESS_NONE);
112
113 dns_name_init(&prev, moffsets);
114 dns_name_init(&next, roffsets);
115
116 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &sregion);
117
118 dns_name_fromregion(&prev, &sregion);
119 isc_region_consume(&sregion, name_length(&prev));
120 RETERR(dns_name_towire(&prev, cctx, target));
121
122 dns_name_fromregion(&next, &sregion);
123 isc_region_consume(&sregion, name_length(&next));
124 return(dns_name_towire(&next, cctx, target));
125}
126
127static inline int
128compare_talink(ARGS_COMPARE) {
129 isc_region_t region1;
130 isc_region_t region2;
131
132 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == rdata2->type);
133 REQUIRE(rdata1->rdclass == rdata2->rdclass);
134 REQUIRE(rdata1->type == dns_rdatatype_talink);
135 REQUIRE(rdata1->length != 0);
136 REQUIRE(rdata2->length != 0);
137
138 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata1, &region1);
139 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata2, &region2);
140 return (isc_region_compare(&region1, &region2));
141}
142
143static inline isc_result_t
144fromstruct_talink(ARGS_FROMSTRUCT) {
145 dns_rdata_talink_t *talink = source;
146 isc_region_t region;
147
148 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_talink);
149 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
150 REQUIRE(talink->common.rdtype == type);
151 REQUIRE(talink->common.rdclass == rdclass);
152
153 UNUSED(type);
154 UNUSED(rdclass);
155
156 dns_name_toregion(&talink->prev, &region);
157 RETERR(isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
158 dns_name_toregion(&talink->next, &region);
159 return(isc_buffer_copyregion(target, &region));
160}
161
162static inline isc_result_t
163tostruct_talink(ARGS_TOSTRUCT) {
164 isc_region_t region;
165 dns_rdata_talink_t *talink = target;
166 dns_name_t name;
167 isc_result_t result;
168
169 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_talink);
170 REQUIRE(target != NULL);
171 REQUIRE(rdata->length != 0);
172
173 talink->common.rdclass = rdata->rdclass;
174 talink->common.rdtype = rdata->type;
175 ISC_LINK_INIT(&talink->common, link);
176
177 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &region);
178
179 dns_name_init(&name, NULL);
180 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
181 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
182 dns_name_init(&talink->prev, NULL);
183 RETERR(name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &talink->prev));
184
185 dns_name_fromregion(&name, &region);
186 isc_region_consume(&region, name_length(&name));
187 dns_name_init(&talink->next, NULL);
188 result = name_duporclone(&name, mctx, &talink->next);
189 if (result != ISC_R_SUCCESS)
190 goto cleanup;
191
192 talink->mctx = mctx;
193 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
194
195 cleanup:
196 if (mctx != NULL)
197 dns_name_free(&talink->prev, mctx);
198 return (ISC_R_NOMEMORY);
199}
200
201static inline void
202freestruct_talink(ARGS_FREESTRUCT) {
203 dns_rdata_talink_t *talink = source;
204
205 REQUIRE(source != NULL);
206 REQUIRE(talink->common.rdtype == dns_rdatatype_talink);
207
208 if (talink->mctx == NULL)
209 return;
210
211 dns_name_free(&talink->prev, talink->mctx);
212 dns_name_free(&talink->next, talink->mctx);
213 talink->mctx = NULL;
214}

216static inline isc_result_t
217additionaldata_talink(ARGS_ADDLDATA) {
218 UNUSED(rdata);
219 UNUSED(add);
220 UNUSED(arg);
221
222 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_talink);
223
224 return (ISC_R_SUCCESS);
225}

227static inline isc_result_t
228digest_talink(ARGS_DIGEST) {
229 isc_region_t r;
230
231 REQUIRE(rdata->type == dns_rdatatype_talink);
232
233 dns_rdata_toregion(rdata, &r);
234 return ((digest)(arg, &r));
235}

238checkowner_talink(ARGS_CHECKOWNER) {
239
240 REQUIRE(type == dns_rdatatype_talink);
241
242 UNUSED(name);
243 UNUSED(type);
244 UNUSED(rdclass);
245 UNUSED(wildcard);
246
247 return (true);

254

257
258 return (true);

262casecompare_talink(ARGS_COMPARE) {
